{"tid":1175371,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"人愈大發覺生得樣衰真係原罪","createTime":"2019-05-28T13:26:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T14:39:03.000Z","uid":172607,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7a1674ba05a38303ff03597998d540d81ad376ef","tid":1175371,"uid":172607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:26:37.000Z","msg":"由細到大 見到有啲生得樣衰嘅同學<br />\n連老師會恥笑佢地<br />\n同學又唔會同佢地玩<br />\n結果就變咗孤獨精<br />\n<br />\n到大啲好彩入到大學<br />\n應該係拍拖出pool黃金時機<br />\n靚仔靚女換左幾次男女朋友<br />\n生得樣衰都仲係A0<br />\n<br />\n出嚟做嘢搵工 hr見到你<br />\n直情唔會請你<br />\n大家人工一樣 點解唔請個靚仔靚女啲？<br />\n<br />\n就連風水玄學<br />\n根本就係搵靚仔靚女做標準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鼻梁低 鼻扁 就會話呢種人唔會發達<br />\n鼻高眼大 就一定係富貴之相<br />\n單眼皮眼細 就會話你陰險 心計重<br />\n<br />\n一句講哂<br />\n其實基本上樣衰條命都衰過人<br />\n我都可以做風水玄學大師了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e5d6f2341394b4b84d72e07e0616fb136d3eb6e","tid":1175371,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:27:16.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"26cc897e8695a5636ec1ab0e831686510ebcb925","tid":1175371,"uid":127929,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:28:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EAWk9qE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEAWk9qE.gif&h=b038f430&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d8ced4a500b5245e97d4ca4dec275ac619a538cb","tid":1175371,"uid":161190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:28:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aec191aa5b7d7addda8cb9360486fec7fa282c11","tid":1175371,"uid":101455,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:30:07.000Z","msg":"未必架，樣靚既，啱啱識會對佢好有好感。但時間耐咗，就睇到人既性格缺陷。往往同你啱傾既朋友都未必係你一開頭有好感既人。始終都係會睇性格同修養。你唔洗咁灰心架，總會有適合既人。"},{"pi